name: Rose
description:
These ladies were created with hand drawn line work, acrylic paint and a variety of plant life compiled digitally. 

For sale are 8"x10" Giclee prints, printed on Allure Rag 100% cotton, Acid-Free, Archival fine art paper.

Each print will be signed and shipped flat with board backing in a bend-proof envelope.
